Name: Puzzle Girls: Cute
About the game: Puzzle Girls: Cute is a puzzle game, in which all you need is to swap tiles, in order to complete the pictured artwork. A relaxing puzzle game to have fun with. Features: A selection of puzzle art to enjoy. Complete Set Levels to unlock hard sets. Level 1 Puzzles = 6 Pieces. Level 2 Puzzles = 12 Pieces & Rotated Pieces. Level 3 Puzzles = 18 Pieces, Rotated Pieces & Flipped Pieces. Three different sets of artwork puzzles. Lazy mode for those who cant be bothered. One handed gaming for easier play !
